These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, photographer
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, american
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter
1. the photographer is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the scientist is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate      | milk    |
| Job           | photographer | scientist |
| Nationality   | egyptian       | american  |
| Transport     | helicopter      | scooter     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, cabbage
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, jazz
2 different pets are kept: rat, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, tram
1. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | cabbage | pineapple |
| Music-Genre   | ambient       | jazz         |
| Pet           | mouse     | rat         |
| Transport     | tram    | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, collecting
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, librarian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | collecting          | baking |
| Job           | librarian | lawyer     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic            | hip-hop         |
| Transport     | snowmobile         | skateboard   |

