The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, techno
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog
1. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | techno |
| Pet           | goldfish | dog    |

