.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, nectarine
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, country
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person eating raspberry is the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of reggae is the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | water     | almond-milk |
| Food          | nectarine   | raspberry |
| Music-Genre   | country     | reggae     |
| Transport     | helicopter | quad-bike     |

 